  <title translate="true">CHD Objects</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading2_atoc_"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">CHD Objects</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Use the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Show_or_Hide_Objects_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Show and Hide Objects</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box to show the objects related to the CHD package (under &quot;MODFLOW Features&quot;) and hide all the other objects.  Three objects define the CHD Boundaries (fig. </text><conditional-text type="IF" value="CHM,HLP,HXS,HTML,DEMO,USER1,USER2,USER3"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">81</text><conditional-text type="ELSE"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">36</text><conditional-text type="END"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">).  Make sure </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Object|Select Objects</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> is selected and double click on the point object on the upper left corner of the grid.  In the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Object_Properties_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Object Properties</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box, select the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MODFLOW_Features_Tab" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">MODFLOW Features</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> tab. The object uses the starting and ending times of the single stress period.  (If there were more than one stress period, the times could encompass several stress periods.)  The starting and ending heads were both set to 30.  Two parameters are defined for the CHD package, but this object does not use either of them (fig. </text><conditional-text type="IF" value="CHM,HLP,HXS,HTML,DEMO,USER1,USER2,USER3"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">82</text><conditional-text type="ELSE"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">37</text><conditional-text type="END"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">).  Click on </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Cancel</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> to close the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Object_Properties_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Object Properties</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box.</text></para>
